text: Typhoon Abby known in the Philippines as Typhoon Diding was significant meteorological event that impacted parts of East Asia in 1983 forming in the Western Pacific Ocean. Typhoon Abby was the first typhoon of the 1983 Pacific typhoon season. == Meteorological history == Typhoon Abby made widespread flooding across Japan Category:1980s in weather
title: Typhoon Abby (1983)
